@startuml
title PatientJourney Lifecycle

state ACTIVE
state SUSPENDED
state COMPLETED

[*] --> ACTIVE : assignPatientJourney

ACTIVE --> SUSPENDED : suspend
SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE : resume
ACTIVE --> COMPLETED : complete
SUSPENDED --> COMPLETED : complete

ACTIVE --> ACTIVE : SWITCH_TEMPLATE\n(change template\n& optional date reset)

note right of ACTIVE
  Transitions enforced by
  updatePatientJourneyStatus
  in src/api/service/
  patientJourneys.ts
end note

note bottom of ACTIVE
  SWITCH_TEMPLATE modifies
  journeyTemplateId and
  optionally resets startDate.
  Recorded in modifications[].
end note

@enduml
